\
\pard\tx720\tx1008\pardeftab720\ri0\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Humans are not the only race in the world of THE BARD'S TALE. others are more magically inclined, stronger and smarter. Part of the fun of a fantasy role-playing game is getting to know these different races, and forming your party accordingly. The races and their descriptions are:\
\pard\tx720\tx1008\pardeftab720\li1008\fi-1008\ri0\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 HUMAN: While possibly being of hardier stock, This caracter is nonetheless like you or me.\
\pard\tx720\tx1008\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\ri0\sa240\partightenfactor0
