\cf0 MONK: a martial artist, an almost inhuman fighting machine trained to fight without weapons or armor. The monk can use them, but, at higher levels particulary, often does better without.\
CONJURER: one of the 4 classes of Magic Users, Conjurers deal in the physical creation and manifestation of real things (like fire,light,healing).\
